It's my sock, dad. What's the problem?

7
00:00:18,603 --> 00:00:20,393
The problem is I found
it on your bathroom floor.

8
00:00:20,394 --> 00:00:21,738
Now, if you're gonna live with me,

9
00:00:21,739 --> 00:00:23,474
