00:00:23,475 --> 00:00:26,996
looking like the
aftermath of a Roman orgy.

11
00:00:27,863 --> 00:00:30,060
Dad, I do a pretty good job
of cleaning up around here.

12
00:00:30,061 --> 00:00:31,912
