and she made all of her bridesmaids

51
00:02:10,639 --> 00:02:11,802
pay for these hideous dresses

52
00:02:11,803 --> 00:02:13,635
and these super-expensive makeovers.

53
00:02:13,636 --> 00:02:15,029
